README for slotplan
==================

About
-----

slotplan is a web app to manage a barcamp slot plan.


Prerequisites
-------------

Python    http://www.python.org


Installation
------------

Unzip the file, then at the command line run

    python setup.py install


Documentation
-------------

To read the API documentation, open a shell / DOS window, navigate to the
slotplan directory, and run

    pydoc slotplan

You can create a HTML version using

    pydoc -w slotplan


License
-------

slotplan is licensed under the GPL. See the file COPYING for details.


